import React from 'react'
import ReactDOM from 'react-dom'
import './index.css'
import App from './App'
import { BrowserRouter } from "react-router-dom"
import { Provider } from 'react'
import store from './redux/store'

ReactDOM.render(
  <Provider store = {store}>
  <BrowserRouter>
  <App />
  </BrowserRouter>,
  </Provider>,
 
  document.getElementById('root')
)
